      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is in the oven, trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Combine your <strong>shredded red cabbage</strong>, <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion</strong> (save a little for garnish), your<strong> wholegrain mustard</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>cider vinegar</strong> and most of your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)<strong> </strong>in a bowl and season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
