    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>cucumber </strong>into batons</p><p>Chop your <strong>dill </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add the <strong>cucumber batons</strong>, <strong>chopped dill </strong>and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>cider vinegar</strong> to a bowl and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Stir everything together and set aside – this is your<strong> quick-pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
