    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s] </strong>in half</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced ciabatta</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 3-4 min or until toasted and charred, then set aside until serving</p>",
