    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>sriracha</strong>, <strong>remaining cayenne pepper</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and <strong>remaining ground paprika </strong>with the <strong>remaining natural yoghurt</strong></p><p>Pour in <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>pickling liquid</strong> from the<strong> quick-pickled cucumber</strong> (discard the rest of the pickling liquid!) and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> hot sauce</strong></p>",
