    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Nashville-style hot free range chicken</strong> over the <strong>toasted ciabatta slice </strong>with<strong> quick-pickled cucumber</strong> and <strong>slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>hot sauce</strong> over the chicken</p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
